WEBVTT

00:00:10.115 --> 00:00:13.865
We are honored to welcome
Police General Phakphum Ratchanon.

00:00:14.195 --> 00:00:19.345
The Deputy Commissioner General is here
to give an address and present your certificates

00:00:20.315 --> 00:00:27.025
I apologize in advance if
my daughter causes any trouble during training.

00:00:29.315 --> 00:00:32.305
I can’t be on the same side as
someone who tried to have me killed.

00:00:32.315 --> 00:00:35.385
But didn't we use to be on the same side?

00:00:35.595 --> 00:00:40.105
I want you to provide security
for my daughter during the holidays.

00:00:40.115 --> 00:00:40.885
Vicky.

00:01:01.195 --> 00:01:05.545
- Hello! Welcome. Um... how many in your party?
- Oh.

00:01:06.515 --> 00:01:08.965
- What can I get for you?
- I’m here to see Ms. Vicky.

00:01:09.355 --> 00:01:12.685
Oh, um... Ms. Vicky?

00:01:12.955 --> 00:01:14.765
Ms. Vicky,

00:01:16.195 --> 00:01:19.485
She’s busy right now.
Would you like to wait?

00:01:20.275 --> 00:01:21.065
That long?

00:01:21.195 --> 00:01:24.385
Well... it will probably take a while.

00:01:24.835 --> 00:01:29.415
If it's urgent, just leave a message. I'll tell her.

00:01:29.635 --> 00:01:33.895
- That's fine. Just tell her Bowontat stopped by.
- Sure.

00:01:36.235 --> 00:01:36.885
Ok.

00:02:12.475 --> 00:02:18.305
(I came to Vicky's shop as you told me to.)

00:02:43.315 --> 00:02:44.845
I told you not to stare.

00:02:58.635 --> 00:03:00.845
I want to stare, so what?

00:03:56.595 --> 00:03:57.525
You know that, right?

00:03:58.715 --> 00:04:00.245
What will happen if you stare at me?

00:04:02.595 --> 00:04:04.205
So, don't do it again.

00:04:16.715 --> 00:04:17.325
Oh.

00:05:02.195 --> 00:05:03.325
I warn you.

00:09:37.875 --> 00:09:38.805
Mali.

00:09:39.805 --> 00:09:42.565
- Mali.
- Yes?

00:09:43.295 --> 00:09:45.205
Who put the Clean Up sign over there?

00:09:45.875 --> 00:09:47.485
Oh, It's me.

00:09:47.995 --> 00:09:48.925
Why?

00:09:49.635 --> 00:09:50.565
Why do you put it there?

00:09:52.195 --> 00:09:53.085
Nothing.

00:09:53.795 --> 00:09:54.725
Nothing?

00:09:55.075 --> 00:09:57.045
No... nothing, nothing.

00:09:57.925 --> 00:10:03.405
So, have you and Captain Tarn done with the boxes?

00:10:06.275 --> 00:10:06.925
Um.

00:10:07.475 --> 00:10:12.445
Wow, you're both sweat.
Is the AC broken or something?

00:10:12.995 --> 00:10:13.785
And...

00:10:14.275 --> 00:10:16.935
Ugh, you talk too much!
Just go put these away.

00:10:17.915 --> 00:10:21.585
Wait, Mr. Bowontat stopped by earlier.

00:10:23.475 --> 00:10:24.965
Mr. Bowontat.

00:10:25.795 --> 00:10:26.525
Yes.

00:10:29.115 --> 00:10:30.305
Hey, stop.

00:10:31.955 --> 00:10:32.825
Hey.

00:10:35.115 --> 00:10:38.785
This is Mr. Bowontat.
He's the son of Minister Burin.

00:10:41.235 --> 00:10:42.205
What was he here for?

00:10:42.835 --> 00:10:45.885
He just asked me to tell you that

00:10:45.965 --> 00:10:48.515
He just dropped by and then left right away.

00:10:50.155 --> 00:10:52.765
- He just came and left... just like that?
- That's right.

00:10:56.235 --> 00:10:58.415
Looks like someone left a surprise for you.

00:11:00.115 --> 00:11:02.065
(Enjoy your work, Captain Tarn.)
(Bowontat Nanthiphak)

00:11:02.075 --> 00:11:03.405
Enjoy your work,

00:11:03.995 --> 00:11:05.365
Captain Tarn.

00:11:08.835 --> 00:11:11.125
Bowontat Nanthiphak.

00:11:13.675 --> 00:11:14.725
What is your deal?

00:11:15.115 --> 00:11:17.795
Since when did you start
hanging out with a politician's son?

00:11:25.675 --> 00:11:27.815
How long have you known Mr. Bowontat?

00:11:29.995 --> 00:11:31.715
You mean Mr. Bawontat?

00:11:32.195 --> 00:11:36.295
I met him when he brought me
flowers on the day I finished the VIP course.

00:11:36.875 --> 00:11:38.125
I'm confused too.

00:11:39.155 --> 00:11:39.625
Oh.

00:11:40.165 --> 00:11:44.195
Oh, Minister Burin actually sent
flowers when I first opened the shop.

00:11:44.555 --> 00:11:46.325
But back then, my dad didn't say anything about it.

00:11:46.555 --> 00:11:49.925
But with Bowontat, Dad wasn't okay at all.

00:11:50.035 --> 00:11:51.525
He told me to be careful.

00:11:54.315 --> 00:11:55.445
Why?

00:11:55.955 --> 00:11:57.285
What did the Deputy Commissioner say?

00:11:58.635 --> 00:12:01.685
Dad thinks those two father and son

00:12:01.715 --> 00:12:04.465
likely have some sort of bad intention toward him.

00:12:04.645 --> 00:12:07.295
And that they might use me as a tool.

00:12:10.075 --> 00:12:14.105
I think he might have stepped on someone's toes,

00:12:14.555 --> 00:12:17.445
or maybe he just has some old enemies.

00:12:19.515 --> 00:12:20.645
That's normal.

00:12:23.075 --> 00:12:25.045
As a police officer yourself,

00:12:25.795 --> 00:12:29.105
you should know that this job
naturally comes with enemies.

00:12:30.915 --> 00:12:34.195
A good cop is an enemy to the bad guys.

00:12:34.795 --> 00:12:37.295
And a bad cop is an enemy to the good ones.

00:12:38.195 --> 00:12:39.075
Right?

00:12:47.515 --> 00:12:48.455
Vicky.

00:12:53.475 --> 00:12:54.555
Hello, Deputy Commissioner.

00:12:56.435 --> 00:12:57.655
Dad.

00:13:05.915 --> 00:13:07.955
You must be tired.
Go take a shower, sweetie.

00:13:08.115 --> 00:13:09.505
I'll see the Captain out myself.

00:13:17.955 --> 00:13:18.985
Alright then.

00:13:35.555 --> 00:13:37.105
I have a favor to ask you.

00:13:39.275 --> 00:13:42.845
A favor from a superior usually means an order.

00:13:47.235 --> 00:13:50.455
Then let’s call it asking
for your cooperation instead.

00:14:02.475 --> 00:14:03.985
I have colon cancer.

00:14:05.835 --> 00:14:08.355
It's in the early stages. Still operable.

00:14:10.555 --> 00:14:12.685
This is serious, sir. You should tell Vicky.

00:14:18.595 --> 00:14:20.575
Vicky already lost her mother to cancer.

00:14:21.715 --> 00:14:23.405
I don't want her to be terrified.

00:14:24.995 --> 00:14:27.595
I don't want her to live in fear of losing me too.

00:14:31.835 --> 00:14:34.575
I told Vicky I'll be away for
a week for an overseas meeting.

00:14:35.715 --> 00:14:37.025
While I’m in surgery

00:14:37.635 --> 00:14:38.815
and recovery.

00:14:40.195 --> 00:14:42.085
I want you to stay with her and keep her company.

00:14:43.035 --> 00:14:45.285
You've seen it yourself
even the Police Headquarters

00:14:46.115 --> 00:14:47.145
isn't safe.

00:14:54.395 --> 00:14:56.765
hat metal box was completely full of documents.

00:14:56.795 --> 00:14:58.625
There’s no way it could have just fallen on its own.

00:14:59.275 --> 00:15:00.505
I am truly sorry.

00:15:00.735 --> 00:15:03.645
We really have no idea
where that metal box came from.

00:15:03.995 --> 00:15:05.675
Could we see the CCTV footage?

00:15:07.755 --> 00:15:10.155
Uh, the CCTV on this floor is out of order.

00:15:10.555 --> 00:15:11.765
The system is currently being upgraded.

00:15:15.915 --> 00:15:19.325
No problem. I'll take care of Vicky.

00:15:20.915 --> 00:15:22.035
Thanks a lot.

00:15:23.695 --> 00:15:25.805
My daughter and I trust you.

00:15:29.435 --> 00:15:30.285
It's late.

00:15:30.955 --> 00:15:32.305
Go get some rest.

00:15:57.755 --> 00:16:01.495
From what you’ve told me,
I don't think he's a bad person.

00:16:02.515 --> 00:16:06.545
If he’d truly helped my father,
he wouldn't be dead.

00:16:09.195 --> 00:16:11.095
But I want you to consider this point.

00:16:14.395 --> 00:16:17.715
Vicky has been threatened twice already, right?

00:16:18.915 --> 00:16:19.655
Um.

00:16:20.275 --> 00:16:22.355
And do you think Vicky actually has enemies?

00:16:22.915 --> 00:16:24.945
Someone as harmless as her?

00:16:25.515 --> 00:16:26.535
It’s unlikely.

00:16:27.635 --> 00:16:30.315
- It’s probably her father’s enemies.
- Ok.

00:16:31.275 --> 00:16:36.345
And what kind of person has a grudge against
the father but target the daughter instead?

00:16:37.195 --> 00:16:40.375
If you fight a bad guy, you're the good guy, right?

00:16:43.595 --> 00:16:45.355
Thugs fighting thugs happens all the time.

00:16:47.235 --> 00:16:52.845
Aside from your father's case, Phakphum is
known to be clean and out of any shady business.

00:16:53.435 --> 00:16:54.595
Maybe

00:16:54.795 --> 00:16:57.005
there’s more to this than we know.

00:17:04.675 --> 00:17:05.355
Hey, Pete.

00:17:05.755 --> 00:17:07.175
Some unknown number is calling me.

00:17:07.315 --> 00:17:08.695
Probably a scammer.

00:17:09.235 --> 00:17:10.305
Go get them.

00:17:11.195 --> 00:17:12.575
Alright, I'm going to take a shower.

00:17:13.875 --> 00:17:14.935
Ok, bye.

00:17:19.475 --> 00:17:20.865
Hello, Captain.

00:17:22.115 --> 00:17:24.015
I’m so glad you picked up.

00:17:25.395 --> 00:17:27.545
Did you like the flowers I sent you?

00:17:28.835 --> 00:17:33.415
I wasn’t sure if a capable woman
like you would appreciate something like this.

00:17:34.435 --> 00:17:36.105
But I figured,

00:17:36.755 --> 00:17:40.315
beautiful women always go well with flowers.

00:17:40.635 --> 00:17:41.455
Right?

00:17:43.595 --> 00:17:45.615
Is my number really that easy to find?

00:17:47.995 --> 00:17:49.405
Not exactly easy, no.

00:17:49.875 --> 00:17:52.925
But for someone like me,
once I set my mind to something.

00:17:53.075 --> 00:17:54.905
nothing is beyond my reach.

00:17:56.515 --> 00:17:58.045
How impressive.

00:17:59.195 --> 00:18:02.265
If you don't have anything else, I’m hanging up.

00:18:02.875 --> 00:18:05.565
I just got home, and I'm exhausted.

00:18:07.115 --> 00:18:09.165
My apologies for bothering you.

00:18:09.875 --> 00:18:10.875
Good night.

00:18:23.475 --> 00:18:25.305
Huh? What?

00:18:26.435 --> 00:18:27.685
And who exactly is she protecting?

00:18:28.835 --> 00:18:30.875
Huh? Vicky?

00:18:31.025 --> 00:18:31.985
Vicky.

00:18:35.795 --> 00:18:39.225
(All eyes on Bowontat & Vicky: Political
and Police heirs—the next power couple)

00:18:39.235 --> 00:18:40.305
Vicky.

00:19:04.995 --> 00:19:05.785
Anya.

00:19:06.435 --> 00:19:07.885
I miss you.

00:19:09.875 --> 00:19:10.745
I’m tired.

00:19:13.555 --> 00:19:15.145
said, I'm tired!

00:19:15.475 --> 00:19:16.565
Enough.

00:19:17.435 --> 00:19:19.215
I said enough!

00:19:21.235 --> 00:19:22.365
What’s wrong with you?

00:19:23.115 --> 00:19:25.235
- Huh?
- I’m not feeling well.

00:19:26.555 --> 00:19:29.385
If you're tired, go rest. I'm heading out.

00:19:31.595 --> 00:19:33.075
You came to see me

00:19:33.715 --> 00:19:34.855
just because you wanted

00:19:35.515 --> 00:19:37.185
But now that you know I'm sick,

00:19:37.635 --> 00:19:39.015
you're just going to leave?

00:19:43.235 --> 00:19:44.765
I’m exhausted.

00:19:45.195 --> 00:19:46.885
Why do you have to start a fight now?

00:19:47.475 --> 00:19:48.705
You’re a doctor.

00:19:49.355 --> 00:19:52.705
If you’re sick, go to the hospital or get some sleep.

00:19:53.555 --> 00:19:54.765
You’re the one who should know,

00:19:55.395 --> 00:19:56.285
not me.

00:20:01.195 --> 00:20:02.485
I’m pregnant. It's yours.

00:20:03.835 --> 00:20:05.175
With me?

00:20:06.625 --> 00:20:09.725
Who else? It’s only ever been you.

00:20:10.355 --> 00:20:11.945
How did you let this happen?

00:20:12.955 --> 00:20:15.245
Didn't we have an agreement?

00:20:17.155 --> 00:20:20.885
- That this was no strings attached.
- Yes, we did.

00:20:20.995 --> 00:20:24.865
It happened.
Are you really not taking responsibility?

00:20:25.635 --> 00:20:26.655
Then get rid of it.

00:20:27.355 --> 00:20:28.465
I'll pay for it.

00:20:30.955 --> 00:20:31.925
You,

00:20:33.155 --> 00:20:34.925
I told you everything.

00:20:35.435 --> 00:20:38.275
Even the unethical things about Phakphum.

00:20:38.555 --> 00:20:40.835
Because I thought we had a future together.

00:20:41.035 --> 00:20:43.545
But you just used me.

00:20:44.475 --> 00:20:45.955
Calm down first.

00:20:46.875 --> 00:20:47.965
We'll talk later,

00:20:48.635 --> 00:20:49.475
okay?

00:20:52.315 --> 00:20:54.295
You’re going to see Vicky, aren’t you?

00:20:57.795 --> 00:20:59.545
Have you been spying on me?

00:21:01.075 --> 00:21:02.815
You're not my wife.

00:21:03.315 --> 00:21:04.425
You have no right.

00:21:05.995 --> 00:21:07.565
You bastard!

00:21:10.955 --> 00:21:12.335
You dare slap me?

00:21:14.115 --> 00:21:15.105
- Huh?
- Let go!

00:21:15.115 --> 00:21:16.505
- Anya!
- Let go!

00:21:16.515 --> 00:21:17.945
- You dare slap me?
- Let go!

00:21:17.955 --> 00:21:18.825
Come here!

00:21:18.875 --> 00:21:20.345
- Let go!
- Come here!

00:21:41.715 --> 00:21:42.665
Ouch!

00:21:58.555 --> 00:21:59.985
Anya!!

00:22:02.235 --> 00:22:05.025
You dare hurt me? Huh?

00:22:05.075 --> 00:22:05.895
Let go.

00:22:06.435 --> 00:22:06.945
Come here!

00:22:08.195 --> 00:22:09.545
- Let go!
- Come here!

00:22:18.755 --> 00:22:19.745
Excuse me, sir.

00:22:27.435 --> 00:22:29.535
Your blood pressure is normal.

00:22:41.435 --> 00:22:42.475
All set.

00:22:47.435 --> 00:22:48.795
P'ma, Any updates?

00:22:48.835 --> 00:22:51.695
Texted her, but no read.
She was just replying last night, though.

00:22:52.195 --> 00:22:54.115
I wonder if she’s feeling unwell?

00:22:54.235 --> 00:22:58.995
But Dr. Ann never flaked before.
Tell the chief?

00:22:59.515 --> 00:23:03.025
Um... Dr. Noey is in the same condo.
Try calling her?

00:23:03.155 --> 00:23:05.975
But today is Dr. Noey's
day off. Wouldn't that be a bother?

00:23:06.035 --> 00:23:09.095
that’s even better!
We can ask her to go check on Dr. Anya at her room.

00:23:21.755 --> 00:23:23.215
This is the outfit, sir.

00:23:24.595 --> 00:23:26.795
A meal will be served shortly.

00:23:26.915 --> 00:23:29.905
And after noon, you’ll need to
start fasting no food or water, okay?

00:23:30.315 --> 00:23:32.445
And has Dr. Anya not arrived yet?

00:23:33.635 --> 00:23:34.475
Umm...

00:23:35.155 --> 00:23:36.645
she should be here shortly.

00:23:46.115 --> 00:23:47.405
Does something feel off to you?

00:23:49.635 --> 00:23:51.005
I’ll check on it.

00:23:56.795 --> 00:23:57.855
P'Ann.

00:23:59.955 --> 00:24:00.985
P'Ann.

00:24:01.795 --> 00:24:02.975
P'Ann.

00:24:15.435 --> 00:24:18.285
P'Ann, please open the door.

00:24:19.715 --> 00:24:20.975
P'Ann.

00:24:22.535 --> 00:24:23.925
P'Ann.

00:24:31.395 --> 00:24:32.755
P'Ann.

00:24:45.835 --> 00:24:46.965
P'Ann.

00:24:56.195 --> 00:24:57.265
P'Ann.

00:25:06.715 --> 00:25:07.825
P'Ann.

00:25:18.835 --> 00:25:19.965
P'Ann.

00:25:29.075 --> 00:25:30.065
P'Ann.

00:25:31.355 --> 00:25:32.485
P'Ann.

00:25:53.515 --> 00:25:54.625
P'Ann.

00:25:55.035 --> 00:25:55.835
P'Ann.

00:26:09.435 --> 00:26:11.565
- You dare hurt me?
- Let go.

00:26:11.755 --> 00:26:15.385
All my life, no one has ever dared
to hurt me. You’re better off dead.

00:26:15.395 --> 00:26:16.945
- Let go!
- Die!

00:26:18.725 --> 00:26:20.005
I told you, let me go!

00:26:24.755 --> 00:26:25.485
Let go!

00:26:47.955 --> 00:26:49.605
I’ve handled everything for you.

00:26:50.075 --> 00:26:52.325
From now on, you don't know that doctor.

00:26:53.555 --> 00:26:54.745
You didn't date.

00:26:55.595 --> 00:26:57.295
You never went to her condo.

00:26:58.435 --> 00:27:01.155
You no longer exist in her world.

00:27:03.435 --> 00:27:04.775
I didn't mean to.

00:27:06.315 --> 00:27:08.525
I... I didn't mean to do it.

00:27:10.225 --> 00:27:12.235
She shouldn't have pushed me to do this.

00:27:18.195 --> 00:27:19.545
Shut up!

00:27:20.795 --> 00:27:22.575
Get a grip on yourself!

00:27:23.795 --> 00:27:26.225
Now is not the time for remorse.

00:27:32.955 --> 00:27:34.505
Let me ask you one more thing.

00:27:35.675 --> 00:27:39.855
Did anyone see you last night?

00:27:49.115 --> 00:27:50.125
Anyone?

00:28:05.835 --> 00:28:06.625
Noey.

00:28:23.995 --> 00:28:25.045
It's alright.

00:28:26.315 --> 00:28:27.425
It's alright.

00:28:30.835 --> 00:28:32.615
It's okay. If there’s something, just tell me.

00:28:44.715 --> 00:28:48.925
I’m in shock. I honestly don't know what to do.

00:28:50.425 --> 00:28:51.725
I understand.

00:28:52.435 --> 00:28:53.755
I understand.

00:28:57.355 --> 00:29:00.425
What about Deputy Phakphum's surgery?

00:29:08.915 --> 00:29:10.715
Another senior surgeon has already taken over.

00:29:18.475 --> 00:29:20.215
I’ll stay the night with you.

00:29:26.195 --> 00:29:27.375
It's alright.

00:29:28.355 --> 00:29:30.405
You’re supposed to be with Vicky.

00:29:30.435 --> 00:29:31.975
I'll stay with you.

00:29:39.275 --> 00:29:40.245
Don't be worried.

00:29:41.675 --> 00:29:43.005
I won't pick a fight with you.

00:29:48.875 --> 00:29:49.915
Stop crying, okay?

00:29:53.475 --> 00:29:56.445
It’s okay, Dr. Noey.

00:29:57.315 --> 00:29:58.775
Stay strong, okay?

00:30:14.915 --> 00:30:15.895
Here,

00:30:16.555 --> 00:30:18.705
here’s your room just over there.

00:30:19.195 --> 00:30:22.475
Let me know if you need anything.
I'll have the maid take care of it for you.

00:30:22.795 --> 00:30:23.615
Okay?

00:30:27.675 --> 00:30:28.895
And what about your room?

00:30:29.755 --> 00:30:31.805
It’s right across from yours. That’s my room.

00:30:33.235 --> 00:30:35.995
You should go unpack and get some rest now.

00:30:37.235 --> 00:30:37.945
Yes.

00:30:54.795 --> 00:30:56.485
I'm at Vicky’s house now.

00:30:57.115 --> 00:31:00.995
Yeah, don't worry about Noey. She's in the shower.

00:31:01.635 --> 00:31:03.345
I already ordered some pizza for her.

00:31:03.835 --> 00:31:06.615
Alright, keep an eye on her for me.

00:31:07.075 --> 00:31:09.865
- Don't get on her nerves.
- Yeah.

00:31:10.235 --> 00:31:12.415
Stop nagging. That's all, bye.

00:31:19.975 --> 00:31:22.285
I thought you said you were
going to stop seeing that rich girl.

00:31:22.635 --> 00:31:24.285
I've given it some thought.

00:31:24.875 --> 00:31:26.735
Being a bodyguard for anyone is the same thing,

00:31:27.155 --> 00:31:29.705
As long as I can get into that
house to find evidence, that's enough.

00:32:26.035 --> 00:32:28.385
Which one? Which one?

00:32:28.675 --> 00:32:31.095
Which one would you like, take your pick.

00:32:31.395 --> 00:32:33.545
A storybook.

00:32:33.635 --> 00:32:37.775
Dear Toad, you are my very best friend.

00:32:37.915 --> 00:32:39.975
Frog went to find the mail bird.

00:32:39.995 --> 00:32:42.685
And said, Please deliver this to Toad.

00:32:42.875 --> 00:32:45.045
I want to got a letter too.

00:32:45.195 --> 00:32:46.585
I'll send you one myself.

00:33:07.795 --> 00:33:09.895
Pete, you glutton!

00:33:10.675 --> 00:33:12.365
You didn't even wait for me!

00:33:19.115 --> 00:33:22.375
- Did you pick the pineapples off the pizza for me?
- Obviously.

00:33:22.795 --> 00:33:25.545
Who the hell orders Hawaiian but hates pineapples?

00:33:27.235 --> 00:33:28.575
Just like you

00:33:28.995 --> 00:33:30.865
ordering pizza but leaving the crust.

00:33:30.915 --> 00:33:32.045
What’s the difference?

00:33:59.035 --> 00:34:01.795
You actually remembered I don't like pineapples?

00:34:02.195 --> 00:34:03.095
Um.

00:34:12.275 --> 00:34:15.375
Take care of yourself, babe.

00:34:15.515 --> 00:34:16.875
Eww, I'm gonna barf!

00:34:17.235 --> 00:34:18.795
I'll stay with you.

00:34:25.915 --> 00:34:26.895
Stop crying.

00:34:31.595 --> 00:34:36.355
You thinking something about me?

00:34:37.155 --> 00:34:38.155
I used to.

00:34:40.195 --> 00:34:43.435
Stop it! We’re friends.

00:34:44.835 --> 00:34:46.215
What did you think I was thinking?

00:34:56.075 --> 00:34:57.465
Well...

00:34:59.115 --> 00:35:00.145
Like...

00:35:03.115 --> 00:35:04.315
That you liked me.

00:35:26.435 --> 00:35:27.665
So full of yourself!

00:35:28.515 --> 00:35:29.995
A cool guy like me

00:35:30.315 --> 00:35:32.945
would never like a nerd like you. No way.

00:35:36.235 --> 00:35:37.905
Who’s the conceited one here, really?

00:35:39.155 --> 00:35:40.395
Don't eat it then.

00:35:40.795 --> 00:35:41.835
Stay out of it!

00:35:54.315 --> 00:35:56.825
What are you doing here?

00:36:06.355 --> 00:36:07.145
Oh.

00:36:08.035 --> 00:36:13.015
I dropped my car keys,
so I came out to look for them.

00:36:13.635 --> 00:36:16.495
I couldn't find the light switch, but...

00:36:17.395 --> 00:36:18.895
I found this photo.

00:36:24.035 --> 00:36:27.225
This is the last family photo we ever took.

00:36:29.115 --> 00:36:32.565
Soon after, my mom was diagnosed with cancer.

00:36:33.035 --> 00:36:36.535
After starting chemo, she refused to take photo.

00:36:37.755 --> 00:36:39.975
And she passed away shortly after that.

00:36:42.275 --> 00:36:43.755
I have colon cancer.

00:36:44.715 --> 00:36:47.145
This is serious, sir. You should tell Vicky.

00:36:48.235 --> 00:36:50.275
Vicky already lost her mother to cancer.

00:36:50.475 --> 00:36:51.905
I don't want her to be terrified.

00:36:52.595 --> 00:36:55.365
I don't want her to live in fear of losing me too.

00:36:56.955 --> 00:36:57.825
Oh.

00:36:58.755 --> 00:37:00.445
You were so young back then.

00:37:01.315 --> 00:37:03.315
How did you manage?

00:37:04.915 --> 00:37:06.775
I grew up with a nanny.

00:37:07.075 --> 00:37:14.765
Dad was rarely around, then sent me to
boarding school in England after primary.

00:37:20.035 --> 00:37:20.745
Hey,

00:37:21.195 --> 00:37:23.625
tell me about your childhood too.

00:37:28.835 --> 00:37:30.485
Let's save that for later, okay?

00:37:32.715 --> 00:37:34.035
It’s getting really late.

00:37:34.475 --> 00:37:35.865
Go to bed now.

00:37:36.835 --> 00:37:37.935
Go on.

00:37:38.195 --> 00:37:39.665
it's late. Hurry up.

00:37:44.835 --> 00:37:45.985
Go.

00:37:46.235 --> 00:37:49.205
Time to sleep. Off you go! Go, go, go.

00:37:50.075 --> 00:37:53.415
- I'm not even sleepy yet.
- Even if you're not, you have to sleep. It's late.

00:37:57.195 --> 00:37:58.415
Go, quick.

00:38:00.995 --> 00:38:01.955
Sweet dreams.

00:38:06.995 --> 00:38:07.835
What?

00:38:14.755 --> 00:38:17.155
Oh, is that it?

00:38:19.435 --> 00:38:20.525
Nope.

00:38:38.675 --> 00:38:39.605
Hey,

00:38:40.075 --> 00:38:41.475
That's enough.

00:38:42.475 --> 00:38:44.905
Go on, quick.

00:38:46.595 --> 00:38:47.485
Sweet dreams.

00:38:49.635 --> 00:38:50.635
Sweet dreams.

00:39:12.795 --> 00:39:14.825
Dr. Anya’s cremation is tomorrow.

00:39:16.835 --> 00:39:18.905
Life is so fragile.

00:39:19.435 --> 00:39:21.095
We were just talking the other day.

00:39:22.835 --> 00:39:24.395
On the last day we spoke,

00:39:24.795 --> 00:39:25.865
she seemed stressed.

00:39:26.795 --> 00:39:29.625
But I had no idea something
so terrible would happen that night.

00:39:31.595 --> 00:39:34.385
Are you sure you don’t want to tell your daughter?

00:39:35.075 --> 00:39:37.075
No, I don't want her to worry.

00:39:37.635 --> 00:39:41.005
Besides, I'll be fine. I trust you, Doctor.

00:39:41.195 --> 00:39:44.625
I was surprised at first
that you kept delaying the surgery.

00:39:44.715 --> 00:39:49.445
So you waited until she had the
right person to take care of her.

00:39:50.275 --> 00:39:51.925
You knew about that?

00:39:52.595 --> 00:39:54.845
I saw it in the gossip news.

00:39:54.955 --> 00:39:56.675
They look like a good match.

00:39:56.835 --> 00:40:00.225
The politician’s son and the top cop’s daughter.

00:40:00.235 --> 00:40:05.255
Oh, you've got it wrong.
They barely know each other.

00:40:08.515 --> 00:40:11.185
Do you know that man, Doctor?

00:40:11.475 --> 00:40:14.325
Uh, just from the news, like I said.

00:40:14.595 --> 00:40:18.625
Sir, I’ve already arranged the room for you.

00:40:18.715 --> 00:40:21.405
- I’ll see you tomorrow around 9 AM.
- Alright.

00:40:22.435 --> 00:40:23.935
I'll take my leave now.

00:40:33.995 --> 00:40:35.085
It's strange.

00:40:35.435 --> 00:40:38.225
Dr. Anya mentioned Mr. Bowontat the other day.

00:40:40.195 --> 00:40:44.515
Anyway, don't any relatives suspect her death?

00:40:45.355 --> 00:40:48.215
Her only living relative left is her older sister.

00:40:49.555 --> 00:40:55.915
But they weren't in touch.
I heard she has no doubts about her death.

00:40:56.315 --> 00:40:57.695
Keep following the doctor's case.

00:40:58.515 --> 00:41:01.755
And find out if Dr. Anya actually knew Mr. Bowontat.

00:41:01.955 --> 00:41:02.895
Yes, sir.

00:41:05.195 --> 00:41:06.825
Regarding the car that tried to attack you,

00:41:07.675 --> 00:41:09.725
my team has tracked it down.

00:41:10.315 --> 00:41:13.165
It fled into Burin’s scrap metal yard.

00:41:14.035 --> 00:41:15.775
The driver confessed

00:41:16.475 --> 00:41:17.635
to being a hired hand.

00:41:18.435 --> 00:41:21.245
The evidence of Burin’s
attempt on your life is undeniable.

00:41:21.355 --> 00:41:25.015
But if the motive is brought to court,

00:41:25.635 --> 00:41:27.985
it will damage your past reputation.

00:41:28.795 --> 00:41:31.265
You should watch your back, Pakphum.

00:41:31.475 --> 00:41:33.915
As a former colleague,

00:41:33.995 --> 00:41:35.745
I'm genuinely concerned.

00:41:36.115 --> 00:41:38.935
I know you're threatening me.

00:41:39.275 --> 00:41:42.185
This is exactly why I suggested
that our families join together.

00:41:42.355 --> 00:41:44.035
If we were on the same side,

00:41:44.515 --> 00:41:46.665
I would have no reason to threaten you.

00:41:54.795 --> 00:41:57.155
The statute of limitations
for that case will expire in a few months.

00:41:58.915 --> 00:42:00.365
If I let it slide,

00:42:02.955 --> 00:42:05.365
Burin won't have to take any responsibility at all?

00:42:32.755 --> 00:42:33.715
Get out!

00:42:34.995 --> 00:42:36.385
Everyone, get out!

00:42:41.355 --> 00:42:42.435
Where are you going?

00:42:45.675 --> 00:42:46.805
Get over here!

00:42:47.635 --> 00:42:49.955
I told you to lay low for a while,

00:42:50.195 --> 00:42:52.095
not to hide like this!

00:42:53.435 --> 00:42:55.215
I'm... I'm scared, Pa.

00:42:56.795 --> 00:42:58.905
Every time I close my eyes, I see...

00:43:03.995 --> 00:43:06.865
How many times do I have to clean up your mess?

00:43:08.835 --> 00:43:10.035
Do you have any idea

00:43:10.795 --> 00:43:14.345
what I had to sacrifice
to wipe your name off the evidence?

00:43:14.795 --> 00:43:17.915
I'm already dealing with
this legislative debate headache,

00:43:17.995 --> 00:43:19.505
and you're still causing trouble!

00:43:21.515 --> 00:43:24.605
Are you trying to choke me to death?

00:43:27.385 --> 00:43:30.515
Go! Drag him back home.

00:43:31.675 --> 00:43:35.675
Get a doctor to check on him.

00:43:36.155 --> 00:43:40.155
- Do whatever it takes to fix him.
- Yes, sir.

00:43:41.955 --> 00:43:46.595
- So, which one is my fan? This one?
- No.

00:43:50.355 --> 00:43:53.475
That one over there, coming to serve us.

00:43:55.355 --> 00:43:57.505
I bet she'll ask for a photo.

00:43:59.595 --> 00:44:00.705
Let's see.

00:44:01.795 --> 00:44:03.135
Here you go.

00:44:03.155 --> 00:44:05.035
Sorry for the wait.

00:44:05.115 --> 00:44:08.225
Here it is, specifically for Captain Tarn.

00:44:08.355 --> 00:44:12.545
I put my heart and soul into this. A Sunny Chai,

00:44:13.435 --> 00:44:16.295
and an iced latte with no sugar, right?

00:44:17.995 --> 00:44:18.755
Thank you.

00:44:21.395 --> 00:44:28.155
And for you, sir, here is the
honey cheesecake and an americano.

00:44:28.635 --> 00:44:29.565
Thank you.

00:44:36.715 --> 00:44:39.495
Um, yes. Happy to help

00:44:43.755 --> 00:44:44.585
Oops.

00:44:45.515 --> 00:44:46.545
how embarrassing.

00:44:47.875 --> 00:44:48.875
What the hell?

00:44:49.625 --> 00:44:50.925
Didn't she recognize me?

00:44:51.515 --> 00:44:53.935
Obviously. You don't look
like your profile picture.

00:44:54.715 --> 00:44:58.055
Everyone says I look much
handsomer in person than on the news.

00:44:59.995 --> 00:45:00.585
Yeah, right.

00:45:10.155 --> 00:45:13.085
This is our new cake. Please try it!

00:45:14.075 --> 00:45:15.065
Thank you.

00:45:15.355 --> 00:45:16.745
Looks delicious!

00:45:24.035 --> 00:45:25.105
Give it a try.

00:45:38.995 --> 00:45:40.025
No.

00:45:52.795 --> 00:45:54.155
Thank you.

00:46:05.275 --> 00:46:06.245
Is it good?

00:46:07.355 --> 00:46:08.355
Yes.

00:46:13.395 --> 00:46:14.565
Please take some rest.

00:46:20.275 --> 00:46:21.865
I'll rest when I'm tired,

00:46:22.955 --> 00:46:25.895
but right now, I'm fully recharged.

00:46:54.035 --> 00:46:58.155
Alright, I'll get back to work then.

00:47:00.035 --> 00:47:01.485
The shop is packed.

00:47:01.995 --> 00:47:03.195
Enjoy the cake.

00:47:08.235 --> 00:47:10.355
Vicky is so crazy about you.

00:47:11.715 --> 00:47:15.075
I think you should forget
the past and just choose her.

00:47:15.715 --> 00:47:17.075
I'd hate to see you throw away a future like this.

00:47:17.795 --> 00:47:20.745
You’re not me.
You wouldn't understand.

00:47:25.275 --> 00:47:26.075
Noey.

00:47:27.915 --> 00:47:28.875
Are you okay?

00:47:29.885 --> 00:47:30.875
Are you okay?

00:47:32.555 --> 00:47:33.355
Go take a seat first.

00:47:47.115 --> 00:47:48.375
Was the funeral crowded?

00:47:49.955 --> 00:47:51.745
Lots of friends and patients.

00:47:52.635 --> 00:47:56.155
As for relatives, only
her older sister and brother- in- law were there.

00:47:57.795 --> 00:48:01.265
But Ann's boyfriend?
He didn't show up at all.

00:48:02.035 --> 00:48:05.055
Even though before she died,
she talked about going on a trip with him.

00:48:08.435 --> 00:48:09.425
Or

00:48:10.155 --> 00:48:11.305
They just broke up?

00:48:11.995 --> 00:48:14.235
Or the breakup stressed her out so much that she...

00:48:14.835 --> 00:48:18.385
I heard people at work
gossiping that P'Ann is pregnant.

00:48:34.555 --> 00:48:37.645
Who’s that guy? The one with the glam look?

00:48:37.995 --> 00:48:42.115
Don't tell anyone about this. It’s not official.

00:48:44.355 --> 00:48:45.615
Okay.

00:48:46.195 --> 00:48:47.155
Noey.

00:48:47.795 --> 00:48:48.925
What's wrong with you?

00:48:58.715 --> 00:49:01.645
That man is P'Ann's boyfriend.

00:49:06.595 --> 00:49:07.765
Vicky.

00:49:10.475 --> 00:49:11.705
Yes.

00:49:14.475 --> 00:49:15.565
Here is some Khao Chae.

00:49:17.955 --> 00:49:19.375
This place is famous!

00:49:19.595 --> 00:49:23.415
I waited in line specifically for you, Vicky.

00:49:24.595 --> 00:49:25.985
Please give some to your father too.

00:49:28.115 --> 00:49:29.415
I’m not sure if he’s up for solid food yet.

00:49:30.675 --> 00:49:31.665
Thank you.

00:49:31.995 --> 00:49:34.735
But my father won't be back for a while.

00:49:34.875 --> 00:49:37.915
I'll just keep it in the fridge for now.

00:49:38.955 --> 00:49:41.745
Next time you visit him,
why don't you invite me along?

00:49:44.635 --> 00:49:45.465
Visit him?

00:49:49.555 --> 00:49:50.545
Oh.

00:49:52.075 --> 00:49:55.655
My dad’s worried since
he can't reach Mr. Phakphum.

00:49:57.955 --> 00:49:59.405
Afraid he might be unwell.

00:50:02.035 --> 00:50:04.525
Uh, he’s actually abroad for a conference.

00:50:05.235 --> 00:50:06.585
Oh, I see.

00:50:07.155 --> 00:50:07.975
My bad.

00:50:09.955 --> 00:50:12.455
Please, make yourself comfortable.

00:50:12.515 --> 00:50:14.245
I need to get back to work now.

00:50:14.715 --> 00:50:16.885
Alright then. I think I'll head out now.

00:50:41.275 --> 00:50:42.935
- Oh! I'm so sorry!
- Ow!

00:50:43.275 --> 00:50:45.185
- I'm sorry, I'm so sorry!
- You piece of shit!

00:50:48.915 --> 00:50:50.525
You dare hurt me?

00:50:51.195 --> 00:50:53.315
Are you fucking blind or what? Huh?

00:50:53.915 --> 00:50:54.665
Do you have any idea

00:50:55.195 --> 00:50:56.455
what happens to people who hurt me?

00:50:56.915 --> 00:50:59.275
what's gonna happen!

00:51:01.395 --> 00:51:03.045
Look at me.

00:51:03.195 --> 00:51:06.195
Do you know what’s coming for you for hurting me?

00:51:09.635 --> 00:51:12.715
I’m so sorry on behalf of my sister, Mr. Bowontat.

00:51:17.915 --> 00:51:20.235
Oh, so you're here, Captain?

00:51:21.235 --> 00:51:23.415
What a pleasure to see you today.

00:51:24.395 --> 00:51:25.485
Eh!

00:51:26.915 --> 00:51:31.635
Heard you're Vicky's bodyguard, is that true?

00:51:32.715 --> 00:51:33.935
How did you know?

00:51:42.755 --> 00:51:43.565
It's okay.

00:51:46.115 --> 00:51:47.445
It's okay.

00:51:47.995 --> 00:51:49.695
We won't let him do anything to you.

00:51:53.715 --> 00:51:54.835
I’d better get going.

00:52:03.395 --> 00:52:05.555
- Ow!
- Sorry.

00:52:30.115 --> 00:52:31.215
P'Ann.

00:52:37.795 --> 00:52:38.885
I'll call you later.

00:53:13.555 --> 00:53:14.825
what's wrong with you, Noey?

00:53:15.995 --> 00:53:17.565
I've been asking for ages, but you kept it quiet.

00:53:18.315 --> 00:53:19.155
Exactly.

00:53:19.915 --> 00:53:22.345
I saw you were off since Bowontat arrived.

00:53:22.915 --> 00:53:25.955
I've wanted to tell you, but the timing was off.

00:53:28.035 --> 00:53:30.055
That guy wasn't just dating P'Ann.

00:53:30.395 --> 00:53:33.095
On the night she died, I saw him at the condo.

00:53:33.475 --> 00:53:35.995
He went into the elevator acting really strange.

00:53:37.355 --> 00:53:38.875
Even though I couldn't see his face clearly,

00:53:39.915 --> 00:53:41.845
I’m certain it was him.

00:53:42.355 --> 00:53:44.015
And his head was bleeding, too.

00:53:47.875 --> 00:53:51.035
Maybe P'Ann didn't commit suicide after all.

00:53:51.795 --> 00:53:53.785
If Bowontat is truly dangerous,

00:53:54.675 --> 00:53:56.855
then you and Vicky need to be careful.

00:54:02.195 --> 00:54:04.905
When I said I liked you, I meant it.

00:54:05.915 --> 00:54:09.465
Tara is the daughter of that
stubborn leader from 19 years ago.

00:54:09.875 --> 00:54:12.715
- Pa, what did you do to Captain Tarn?
- Buried him.

00:54:12.835 --> 00:54:14.035
What happened?

00:54:16.275 --> 00:54:18.025
You still kept this photo?

00:54:19.315 --> 00:54:20.085
Hey,

00:54:20.435 --> 00:54:24.035
Tell me about your childhood.
You've put it off way too many times.

00:54:24.915 --> 00:54:26.925
Why did you hand over the evidence to them?

00:54:26.995 --> 00:54:29.845
Or does the Deputy know who Captain Tara really is?